  description: "\\emph{\'Know ye that time is ever so short, even for those who believed their\n                    mythal afforded them all the time on \\Place{Toril}; I pray that ye learn\n                    better from their mistakes than they did themselves---for the dead know many\n                    things, but grasp truth and grow in knowledge they are rarely able to do.\'\n                    \\right{---\\NPC{Elminster} of \\Place{Shadowdale}, Year of the Gauntlet}}\n                    \\Product[TSR 9558]{The Fall of Myth Drannor} is an accessory detailing those\n                    horrible years encompassing the \\Event{Weeping War}, for use with the\n                    \\Product[TSR 1165]{Cormanthyr: Empire of Elves} book. Herein you will find\n                    the causes of the Fall of that most lyrical of elf cities; highlights of the\n                    twelve campaigns in their most significant battles; copious adventure hooks\n                    for involving player characters in behind-the-scenes activities; and new (or\n                    should we say ancient?) magical items and spells, most of which have been\n                    lost in time.\n                    From the passing of Coronal \\NPC{Eltargrim} to the shattering of the\n                    \\NPC{Khov\'Anilessa}\'s invisible prison to the stand at \\Place{Honorsgate},\n                    the painful history of the \\Event[Fall of Myth Drannor]{Fall} lies within\n                    these pages. Now comes the opportunity for heroes to be made---or become part\n                    of the history in their attempts."
